  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600765388317-7C5EQFQAF9OH101VWXWZ/11a-projectlifebanner1.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Still loving Project Life, even though I am a bit behind on photographing (I'm blaming June gloom for insufficient lighting indoors). A gentle reminder to keep it simple and realize not every single week has to be documented with detail.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"11b-DSC_0142-600x577.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600765455932-KPIDDRYMKVJYYXY47ULO/11b-DSC_0142-600x577.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"11c-DSC_0146-600x562.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600765455969-W15G0N6NYKV0ZN6GC6FL/11c-DSC_0146-600x562.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11d-DSC_0148-600x295.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600765456409-WVA77SRYCTCQ21C1CH1V/11d-DSC_0148-600x295.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11e-DSC_0149-600x370.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600765456582-VBSV9SHCKMTLZE36G03B/11e-DSC_0149-600x370.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"11f-DSC_0151-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600765456979-XKO55J95LQZ28BT75O7C/11f-DSC_0151-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Stayed within a color scheme this week (for the most part), at first unintentionally, then I couldn't get over how cool it looked. I taught in San Diego at Paper Tales and it was wonderful. Christine did such a nice wrap up on <a href=\"http://www.listgirl.com/2012/05/get-crafty-with-amy-tan-class-at-paper.html\">her blog</a>. On a crafty note, I combined a couple stamps - California from the <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2D42298%2FHero%2DArts%2DClear%2DStamps%2FDetail\">USA Studio Calico set</a> and the Love (I only inked up the Love of the I Love stamp) from <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/studio-calico/128290-pieces-of-me-workshop-kit/%3Ffilters%3D_pieces%2Bof%2Bme_\">the Pieces of me kit</a>. Other supplies: <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2D42299%2FHero%2DArts%2DClear%2DStamps%2FDetail\">Weekdays stamps</a>, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/_hello%2520forever_/\">Hello Forever papers</a>, Yellow woodgrain is from <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/jillibean-soup/125329-chicken-dumpling-collection-packs/%3Ffilters%3D_jillibean%2Bsoup_\">this Jillibean Soup collection pack</a>, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/studio-calico/128335-heyday-cameras-mistable-thicker-stickers/%3Ffilters%3D_studio%2Bcalico_\">Mistable camera</a> + <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/studio-calico/127066-taxi-yellow-mister-huey-spray/%3Ffilters%3D_taxi%2Bmister%2Bhuey_%252Fmists-and-sprays\">Yellow mist</a> (which is THE perfect yellow IMHO), paper scraps, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/_alphabean_/stickers/\">favorite alphas at the moment</a> (back in stock at Two Peas!), HeyDay 6X6 paper pad, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/_washi%2520tapes_/%3Fpp%3D300\">washi tapes</a>. And I included my <a href=\"http://static.squarespace.com/static/54763a73e4b0d25603e00ba7/54a756aae4b0f2d6f3befd4e/54a773bfe4b0f2d6f3c1cc6a/1420260287558/washi_tape_pattern_1-2?format=original\">free downloadable washi tape</a> and sized to just under 3\"X4\". You can see all my Project Life posts <a href=\"http://static.squarespace.com/static/54763a73e4b0d25603e00ba7/54a756aae4b0f2d6f3befd4e/54a773bfe4b0f2d6f3c1cc6d/1420260287567/project-life?format=original\">here</a>. And the <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/mn/search/?_encoding=UTF8&amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20&amp;linkCode=ur2&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;field-keywords=project%20life&amp;url=search-alias%3Daps#/ref=nb_sb_noss_1?url=search-alias=aps\">Project Life photo pocket pages</a>are available on Amazon.</p>"
